}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== The S/N of the hub populating this entry is '''CZ81227322'''.
"12412 REV:1.0/1.0MM-LF" and the '''[[Belkin]]''' logo is silkscreened on the board. :The '''[[Alcor Micro]]''' hub IC is marked with the '''ALCOR''' logo, "ALCOR MICRO", "AU9254A21-HAS-NP", "SL8666", and "0726". :The hub is using all '''Canicon''' capacitors.
The power adapter included with the hub appears to be an ''unbranded'' PS0526 (100-240VAC ~ 50/60Hz, 0.5A -> 5VDC 2.5-2.6A).
